      <div class="field-group"><label>Mould Life (cycles) <span title="Al blow moulds: 500k–2M cycles. IBM steel: up to 5M.">ℹ</span></label><input type="number" id="bm-mould-life" step="50000" min="0" value="1000000"/></div>
